612	613	ai_prompts	3b5d8ca2-3418-406f-8f14-46010521a65d	{"id":"3b5d8ca2-3418-406f-8f14-46010521a65d","sort":null,"name":"product-description","status":"in_review","description":"Generate product descriptions that convert","messages":[{"role":"user","text":"# CONTEXT #\\nI need to create a compelling product description for {{ product name }} to be published through our Directus CMS. This product is {{ brief product description }} in the {{ category/industry }} market.\\n\\n# OBJECTIVE #\\nGenerate a complete product description that effectively communicates the key features, benefits, and unique selling points of {{ product name }}. The description should persuade potential customers to make a purchase while providing all necessary product information.\\n\\n# STYLE #\\nThe description should be structured with clear sections highlighting features and benefits. Use bullet points for key specifications and include persuasive language that emphasizes value. Maintain our brand voice while incorporating SEO-friendly keywords.\\n\\n# TONE #\\nThe tone should be {{ enthusiastic/professional/friendly/authoritative }} while remaining authentic and trustworthy. Avoid exaggeration while still highlighting what makes our product special.\\n\\n# AUDIENCE #\\nOur target customers are {{ demographic details }} who {{ pain points/needs }}. They are looking for {{ specific benefits }} and value {{ important factors in purchase decision }}.\\n\\n# RESPONSE #\\nA complete product description with:\\n\\nAn attention-grabbing headline or product name\\nA concise overview paragraph (2-3 sentences)\\nKey features and benefits in bullet form or short paragraphs\\nTechnical specifications where relevant\\nMaterials/ingredients information if applicable\\nUsage instructions or suggestions\\nA compelling call-to-action\\n\\nThe description should be approximately {{ word count }} words in length and optimized for both conversion and SEO, ready for implementation in our Directus CMS."}],"syste